simple status bar only application, that prints the current input/output network usage in mbps, updated every 2 seconds

looks like this:
kbps: http://i42.tinypic.com/1zvbk8n.png (292 kbps input, 12mbps output)
mbps: http://i40.tinypic.com/23sj1tv.png (14mbps input, 0mbps output)

it uses ifmib(4), and very cool icon: http://www.iconarchive.com/show/halloween-icons-by-arrioch/skull-icon.html
